Ines Diers.label: Ines Diers

Ford Hiroshi Konno is an American former competition swimmer, two-time Olympic champion, and former world record-holder in three events.

Allen Stack.label: Allen Stack

Lynne Cox.label: Lynne Cox

Vanja Rogulj is a 3-time Olympics breaststroke swimmer from Croatia. He swam for Croatia at the 2000, 2004 and 2008 Olympics.

Thomas Lejdström is a former Swedish freestyle and medley swimmer, who competed in the 1980 and 1984 Summer Olympics.
